short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get top dental care with Molldrem Family Dentistry. Book same-day appointments online easily

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Since opening Molldrem Family Dentistry in Eden Prairie, MN in June 2004, Dr. Kevin Molldrem has been dedicated to delivering the same exceptional dental care he would want for his own family. With extensive training and experience, Dr. Molldrem and his team expertly and compassionately address each family's unique dental needs.

Committed to continuous education, Dr. Molldrem embraces cutting-edge technologies and minimally invasive treatments to provide top-notch care. Since 1999, he has been transforming patients' lives, helping them achieve healthy, radiant smiles.

Outside the office, Dr. Molldrem enjoys quality time with his three daughters—Georgia, Francesca, and Addison—and their two cats. They love scuba diving, snowboarding, and wakesurfing together.

Experience honest, trustworthy dental care with Dr. Kevin Molldrem, where your family's smile is our top priority.
